ation API"}]},{"type":"text","text":". If you want to understand that API in depth or build a custom decoration style, see the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"Decorations.md","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/Readium\/Highlights"},"doc://Readium/documentation/Readium/Navigator":{"type":"topic","role":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use a Readium Navigator to present the publication to the user. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Navigator"},{"type":"text","text":" renders resources on the screen and offers APIs and user interactions for navigating the contents."}],"url":"\/documentation\/readium\/navigator","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/Readium\/Navigator","title":"Navigator"},"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/uiviewrepresentable":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swiftui\/uiviewrepresentable","titleInlineContent":[{"code":"UIViewRepresentable","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swiftui\/uiviewrepresentable","title":"UIViewRepresentable"},"Preferences.md":{"url":"Preferences.md","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"EPUB navigator preferences"}],"type":"link","identifier":"Preferences.md","title":"EPUB navigator preferences"},"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/picker":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swiftui\/picker","titleInlineContent":[{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swiftui\/picker","title":"Picker"},"doc://Readium/documentation/Readium/NavigatorOverview":{"type":"topic","title":"Navigator Overview","identifier":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/Readium\/NavigatorOverview","role":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn about the architecture, configuration, and usage of the Readium Navigator."}],"url":"\/